      "title": "All three shift to camp",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vasantha Mudalike, Hasanda Gunathilakka and Ven Kalveva Siridamma Thera, who have been detained for 90 days under the Prevention of Terrorism Act, have been shifted to Thangala detention camp.",
        "The Police Media Spokesperson Department announced that they are being investigated by the Criminal Investigation Division and the Anti-Terrorism Division."
      ],
